01:48.608 --> 01:53.405
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:53.405 --> 01:54.448
The gym.

01:54.448 --> 01:57.159
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:57.159 --> 01:58.744
Right here in this setup,

01:58.744 --> 02:00.912
we've got a lot of
different types of steel.

02:00.912 --> 02:02.622
Some of that steel
