02:34.363 --> 02:37.991
and for edge retention
in a bag slice.

02:37.991 --> 02:39.826
You will have ten minutes
to work on your designs.

02:39.826 --> 02:42.663
You will have three hours
to forge your blades.

02:42.663 --> 02:44.206
Good luck, bladesmiths.

02:44.206 --> 02:46.333
Your ten‐minute design window
starts now.

02:46.333 --> 02:48.502
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:48.502 --> 02:50.128
The tests we have coming up

02:50.128 --> 02:54.257
are our 45‐pound plate chop
and a bag slice.

02:54.257 --> 02:57.427
‐ It's gonna be heat‐treat
and edge geometry.

02:57.427 --> 02:59.262
