about drawing out my tang.

08:21.167 --> 08:23.336
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:23.336 --> 08:26.923
It's going pretty good
right now.

08:26.923 --> 08:29.342
I have to lose some meat
off of this,

08:29.342 --> 08:31.177
grind it to shape,
and heat treat it.

08:31.177 --> 08:33.054
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:33.054 --> 08:35.682
‐ Braxton's really getting
that blade ground down

08:35.682 --> 08:38.017
to a really fine look,

08:38.017 --> 08:40.562
but it'd be nice to have him
