like a San Mai?

09:12.552 --> 09:15.722
‐ Well, you can sandwich it.
That's one way to do it.

09:15.722 --> 09:17.265
‐ What's the strongest way?

09:17.265 --> 09:19.184
‐ That would probably
be the best,

09:19.184 --> 09:21.644
'cause there's more contact.
‐ More contact, right.

