or come apart.

09:52.050 --> 09:55.345
‐ Kyle taking two pieces
of the tube.

09:55.345 --> 09:57.889
They're pretty thin. He's gonna
have to tack that a lot.

09:57.889 --> 09:59.265
If you just, like,
