10:21.454 --> 10:22.956
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:22.956 --> 10:25.125
<i>‐ I used the San Mai technique</i>

10:25.125 --> 10:26.960
<i>so that the outer shell</i>
<i>of the blade</i>

10:26.960 --> 10:29.504
