<i>into that weight.</i>

10:31.256 --> 10:33.424
She's stuck, baby.
She's stuck.

10:33.424 --> 10:35.301
My welds seem like
they have stuck.

10:35.301 --> 10:36.970
Mother[bleep].

10:36.970 --> 10:38.471
<i>Then I realize</i>
<i>that there was some delams</i>

10:38.471 --> 10:40.181
